item.title: Download
item.description: rust-keylock is delivered as a desktop app, an Android app and a shell app. Here is how you can install what you are interested in: Desktop The desktop application is offered as a Snap. Android You may download the .apk from here and install it yourself on your devices. Please note that the .apk is built and deployed automatically by Travis CI upon each release to ensure that the code being built is publicly available.
